6UFRISEKBM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FKB42QWGPGZGUZME56UFRISEKBM%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN20tjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=a29bc31e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2FKB42QWGPGZGUZME56UFRISEKBM%2F&h=8dff5f70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/KB42QWGPGZGUZME56UFRISEKBM/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n離一離題，投身職場唔係通常形容學生畢業後做野咩，可以當「去番工」咁用嫁咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3e5a002cff1de254a9c1377f9862aa97ee1be6","tid":2411117,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:12:04.000Z","msg":"15年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n誤殺都係20年？"},{"pid":"5b6fbf596eaf4c6ededcac92f26ecdad027e500b","tid":2411117,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"有有冇預謀呢啲睇6師點吹＋個官點睇姐<br />\n窮閪廚房佬冇錢請勁6師＋法官高高在上睇唔起你啲窮撚低下階層咪判重啲囉<br />\n你係社會賢達有錢佬 咪求其社會服務令囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f09ec26f000fe9944920bfe63bcdd7585273acd","tid":2411117,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bdc58425946a87974a4d3ede9a50da777513896","tid":2411117,"uid":183844,"like":72,"dislike":3,"score":69,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T06:18:08.000Z","msg":"噚日車死人都係10個月<br />\n個準則好撚癲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021